I thought this was book and quite liked the idea of drawing Black's Q out prematurely where I could harass it and develop my minor pieces at the same time.  The closest thing my aging book on the French by Alexei Suetin (first published in German 1982, English translation 1988) has is  4... Nd7 5. Nf3 Nf6 6. Nxf6.
